summary:
Hi there,
I am an enthusiastic and adaptable brand, creative and comms strategy consultant with international experience across a broad range of categories (luxury, lifestyle, entertainment, sportswear, fashion, beauty, food, automotive, environmental protection and tech). 

I help brands get recognised and relevant.

I was born in France, spent a lot of my childhood in Mexico and have been lucky to work in Paris, London, Sydney and Amsterdam. I recently moved to Biarritz on the French Atlantic coast where I attempt to perfect my abysmal surfing skills. 
I work remotely and travel if necessary. 

I go to work in the morning to create work that works and that makes a positive cultural impact.
I passionately believe in the importance of teamwork, frequent reality checks, a sense of humour and avoiding bullshit.
And because I also passionately believe in listening more than I talk, I‚Äôm going to stop there.

--
